00:33.041 --> 00:33.986
<i>Ben.</i>

00:35.690 --> 00:38.260
Hey, partner.
Merry Christmas.

00:38.705 --> 00:40.609
When are you gonna
break down and buy a car?

00:41.653 --> 00:44.420
I own 72 rigs.
Why should I buy a car?

00:44.846 --> 00:46.546
And what the hell
are you wearing there?

00:46.570 --> 00:49.520
I know, it's pretty awful.
It's from the Christmas party.

00:49.749 --> 00:52.003
Guess who my Secret Santa was?

00:52.714 --> 00:53.960
- Monk.
- Monk.

00:54.415 --> 00:55.987
I thought you were
gonna fire his ass.

00:56.046 --> 00:58.126
I didn't have the heart.
You know, it's Christmas.

00:58.205 --> 00:59.265
Hell, I'll do it.

00:59.266 --> 01:00.957
It should've been done
a long time ago.

01:01.013 --> 01:02.531
So what's so important?

01:02.532 --> 01:05.866
We're being audited
or the depot burn down or something?

01:12.212 --> 01:13.707
Looks like you were
in my office.

01:13.787 --> 01:15.716
It's our office, Ben.
We're partners, remember?

01:16.041 --> 01:18.131
At least I thought so.
There are forgeries.

01:18.171 --> 01:20.131
Kenneth,
you're an accountant.

01:20.388 --> 01:22.524
You don't know the first
thing about maintenance.

01:22.559 --> 01:24.865
Do I have to call Chicago
and crosscheck these invoices?

01:24.905 --> 01:26.091
Because I will.

01:26.683 --> 01:29.166
You been buying
recycled parts for these rigs

01:29.312 --> 01:30.631
and pocketing
the difference?

01:30.632 --> 01:32.544
I don't believe this.
You know, after 9 years--

01:32.563 --> 01:33.699
It's not just the money.

01:33.940 --> 01:35.627
We have 72 drivers
on the road.

01:35.687 --> 01:38.899
- Now, what if something happens?
- Hey, partner, relax.

01:39.394 --> 01:41.633
Because unless you have proof,
and I mean real proof--

01:41.767 --> 01:43.012
I have proof.

01:44.136 --> 01:47.117
There's proof in every engine
in every truck in the fleet.

01:47.176 --> 01:49.232
You want proof?
You want to see proof?

01:49.266 --> 01:50.532
I know enough.

01:50.884 --> 01:53.533
I know enough,
my friend.

01:54.547 --> 01:55.714
Exhibit "A".

01:56.489 --> 01:57.735
That manifold.

01:58.254 --> 02:00.627
Now according to this,
it's brand-new.

02:00.786 --> 02:03.128
Look at it. The gasket's loose.
It's all rusted out.

02:03.148 --> 02:05.263
If that thing cracks,
the whole engine's gonna blow.

02:05.283 --> 02:06.864
I don't want that
responsibility--

02:11.038 --> 02:12.245
Cut me loose, Ben!

02:16.802 --> 02:18.629
Cut me loose, Ben!

02:19.361 --> 02:20.468
Please!

02:24.078 --> 02:25.561
What are you doing?!

02:44.118 --> 02:46.747
5x09 - Mr. Monk Meets His Dad

02:47.222 --> 02:49.930
